window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>First, the Vermillion Dragon. Then, the Multiverse!</b></p> <p>In the aftermath of the Apocalypse, humanity struggles to survive in a world newly introduced to mysterious particles.</p> <p>Preparing for the moment when Earth's planetary protections will cease and open the planet up to invasion by alien species, Liam and his companions transformed the Beacon, their sanctuary, into a fortress.</p> <p>As the last line of defense, they strive to train and empower the Beacon's residents, raising their levels and strength to withstand the impending onslaught.</p> <p>The coming days will be filled with battles, trading, and a lot of research on how the multiverse works and exactly what the Dominions are.</p> <p>Spearheading the efforts of humanity is... Jon.</p> <p>How? Well... there's only one way to find out.</p>"; 
